snippet.title: Cat TV for Cats to Watch
snippet.description:
Cat TV that will leave your cat utterly spellbound as they witness the non-stop, mesmerising parade of delightful birds and mischievous squirrels gracing our garden with their enchanting presence!

Regular Visitors:
Grey Squirrel
Woodpigeon
Robin
Blackbird
Starling
Coal Tit
Blue Tit
Magpie
Jackdaw
Collared Dove
Carrion Crow

Occasional Visitors:
Nuthatch
Dunnock
Greater Spotted Woodpecker

Rare Visitors:
Blackhat
Wren
Goldcrest
